I have very great
open-source tools.

00:14:22.400 --> 00:14:28.300
That means when you want to build
a website, you can choose really,

00:14:28.300 --> 00:14:31.980
really standard
rock-solid foundations.

00:14:31.980 --> 00:14:37.120
We chose the more or less
standard approach to this Linux,

00:14:37.120 --> 00:14:42.860
